{"type":null,"faqId":38504,"title":"华为钱包","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.1in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><a name=\"_task_oto_service-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> 惠生活</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125473\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”“华为钱包”，在“惠生活”页签，您可以团购附近的美食和电影票，给手机充值还能享受更多优惠。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">2.</span><a name=\"_task_hw_wallet-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">我的钱包</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">使用华为钱包可以快捷安全地购买您喜欢的应用、虚拟游戏道具、主题和壁纸等娱乐内容。使用钱包前，请先根据屏幕提示注册或登录一个华为帐号。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125474\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”“华为钱包”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在“我的钱包”页签，您可以：</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">  </span><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“我的银行卡 &gt; 关联银联卡”，按照屏幕提示完成信用卡的关联。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">  </span><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“设置 &gt; 安全设置 &gt; 手势密码”，开启并设置手势密码，保护您的帐号安全。</span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":1094,"faqType":"生活助手","useful":2,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3784","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Convenient-features","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448685000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":132,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为钱包","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}